<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="wccpilgrimagesite.app">
<body>

  <metal:styleslot fill-slot='style_slot'>
      <style type="text/css" media="all">
        .formTabs{visibility: hidden;}
         
      </style>
</metal:styleslot>

<tal:comment tal:condition="nothing">
    This is a sample view template. It will not be used for rendering the
    content unless activated by creation of a view class with a matching name.
    
    Note that we're using Plone 4 macros. Replace them with Plone 3 macros
    if needed.
</tal:comment>

<metal:main fill-slot="content-core">
  <metal:content-core define-macro="content-core">

      <tal:block repeat="widget view/widgets/values">
          <div class="field" tal:condition="python:widget.__name__ not in ('IDublinCore.title', 'IDublinCore.description', 'title', 'description',)">
              <label tal:content="widget/label" />
              <br />
              <div tal:content="structure widget/render" />
          </div>
      </tal:block>
      
      <!--color page container-->
      <div class="blue-page animated fadeIn">
      
            <!--page header-->
            <header class="content-header blue-bg">
                  <div class="row">
                        <div class="columns small-12 text-center">
                              <div class="logo">
                                    <img src="++theme++wccpilgrimagesite.theme/images/step1.png" alt="What is a pilgrimage?">
                              </div>
                              <h1 tal:content="context/Title">What is a pilgrimage?</h1>
                              <p tal:content="context/Description">Share your thoughts about pilgrimage from your context.</p>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </header>
            
            <!--page content-->
            <section class="content-strip white-bg">
                  <div class="row">
                        <div class="columns small-12 text-center">
                              <h2>A journey of faith</h2>
                              <p>Pilgrimage is common to all the world’s religious traditions. A pilgrimage is a journey of faith, often to a place considered sacred, in order to offer thanks, to atone for wrong-doing, or to seek enlightenment or healing or reconciliation. In the Bible itself are many examples of pilgrimage. As you begin to explore the WCC Pilgrimage of Justice and Peace, consider the nature of pilgrimage in your faith and the faith of others different from you. As you do, share your ideas and experience with others through the comments sections below, by making a video or audio presentation or sharing with others through social media. The resource document that you can download below will help you consider pilgrimage in your own life’s journey or that of your community. To draw others into the conversation in social media use the hashtag #WhatIsAPilgrimage.</p>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </section>
            
            <!--comments-->
            <section class="content-strip white-bg">
                  <div class="row">
                        <div class="columns small-12 text-center">
                              <h2>Your comments</h2>
                              <ul class="comments-list no-bullet" tal:define="brains view/comments_result" tal:condition="brains">
                                    <li tal:repeat="brain brains">
                                          <div class="cl-image-wrapper">
                                                <span class="cl-image" style="background-image: url(++theme++wccpilgrimagesite.theme/images/mussel.png)"></span>
                                                <span class="cl-image-mask">
                                                      <img tal:condition="python: brain.getObject().image" tal:attributes="src python: brain.getPath()+'/@@images/image/mini'">
                                                </span>
                                                <span class="quotes">
                                                      <img alt="Quotes" src="++theme++wccpilgrimagesite.theme/images/quotes.png">
                                                </span>
                                          </div>
                                          <div class="cl-details">
                                                <div class="heart-box">
                                                      <a data-votable="c647a2e88be24f90a42daf23b36793b6"><i class="fa fa-heart"></i></a>
                                                      <span class="heart-number" data-votes-count="c647a2e88be24f90a42daf23b36793b6">5</span>
                                                </div>
                                                <h4 tal:content="python: brain.getObject().title"></h4>
                                                <p tal:content="python: view.datetime_result(brain.getObject().datetime_added)"></p>
                                          </div>
                                          <div class="cl-text">
                                                  <p tal:content="python: brain.getObject().message"></p>
                                          </div>
                                    </li>
                              </ul>
                              
                              <!--<tal:block tal:define="brains view/comments_result" tal:condition="brains">
                                    <table>
                                      <tbody>
                                        <tr tal:repeat="brain brains">
                                          <td>
                                          <img tal:condition="python: brain.getObject().image" tal:attributes="src python: brain.getPath()+'/@@images/image/mini'" width="100px"/>
                                          </td>
                                          <td tal:content="python: brain.getObject().title"></td>
                                          <td tal:content="python: brain.getObject().email"></td>
                                          <td tal:content="python: brain.getObject().message"></td>
                                          <td tal:content="python: view.datetime_result(brain.getObject().datetime_added)"></td>
                                
                                
                                        </tr>
                                      </tbody>
                                    </table>
                              </tal:block>-->
                          
                              <tal:block tal:define="brains view/resources_result" tal:condition="brains">
                                    <table>
                                          <tbody>
                                                <tr tal:repeat="brain brains">
                                            <!--   <td>
                                              <img tal:condition="python: brain.getObject().image" tal:attributes="src python: brain.getPath()+'/@@images/image/mini'" width="100px"/>
                                              </td> -->
                                                      <td tal:content="python: brain['name']"></td>
                                                      <td tal:content="python: brain['email']"></td>
                                                      <td tal:content="python: brain['church']"></td>
                                                      <td tal:content="python: brain['message']"></td>
                                                      <td tal:condition="python: brain['type'] != 'document'" tal:content="python: brain['resource']"></td>
                                                      <td ><a tal:condition="python: brain['type'] == 'document'" tal:attributes="href python: brain['path']+'/view/++widget++form.widgets.document/@@download/'+brain['resource']" tal:content="python: brain['resource']"></a></td>
                                                </tr>
                                          </tbody>
                                    </table>
                                    <div><a tal:attributes="href view/resources_path">View All</a></div><br>
                              </tal:block>
                              
                              <a class="action-button add-comment" tal:attributes="href python:'/'.join(context.getPhysicalPath())+'/++add++wccpilgrimagesite.app.usercomment'">
                                    <span class="ab-circle">+</span>
                                    <br />
                                    <span class="ab-text">Add a comment</span>
                              </a>
                              
                              <!--start comment form-->
                              <div class="add-comment-form">
                                    <form id="form" class="rowlike enableUnloadProtection enableFormTabbing kssattr-formname-++add++wccpilgrimagesite.app.usercomment" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post" action="++add++wccpilgrimagesite.app.usercomment">
                                          <fieldset id="fieldset-default" class="formPanel" style="display: block;">
                                                <legend id="fieldsetlegend-default" style="visibility: hidden; font-size: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 0px; width: 0px; line-height: 0;">Default</legend>
                                                <ul class="small-block-grid-1 medium-block-grid-2">
                                                      <li>
                                                            <div id="formfield-form-widgets-title" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.title empty" data-fieldname="form.widgets.title">
                                                                  <label class="horizontal" for="form-widgets-title">Name
                                                                        <span class="required horizontal" title="Required"></span>
                                                                  </label>
                                                                  <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                                                  <input id="form-widgets-title" class="text-widget required textline-field" type="text" value="" name="form.widgets.title"/>
                                                            </div>
                                                      </li>
                                                      <li>
                                                            <div id="formfield-form-widgets-email" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.email empty" data-fieldname="form.widgets.email">
                                                                  <label class="horizontal" for="form-widgets-email">E-mail
                                                                        <span class="required horizontal" title="Required"></span>
                                                                  </label>
                                                                  <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                                                  <input id="form-widgets-email" class="text-widget required textline-field" type="text" value="" name="form.widgets.email"/>
                                                            </div>
                                                      </li>
                                                      <li>
                                                            <div id="formfield-form-widgets-datetime_added" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.datetime_added" data-fieldname="form.widgets.datetime_added">
                                                                  <label class="horizontal" for="form-widgets-datetime_added">Datetime added
                                                                        <span class="required horizontal" title="Required"></span>
                                                                  </label>
                                                                  <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                                                  <select id="form-widgets-datetime_added-day" class="day datetime-widget required datetime-field" onchange="updateCalendar('#form-widgets-datetime_added');" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-day"></select>
                                                                  <span class="separator">/</span>
                                                                  <select id="form-widgets-datetime_added-month" class="month datetime-widget required datetime-field" onchange="updateCalendar('#form-widgets-datetime_added');" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-month"></select>
                                                                  <span class="separator">/</span>
                                                                  <select id="form-widgets-datetime_added-year" class="year datetime-widget required datetime-field" onchange="updateCalendar('#form-widgets-datetime_added');" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-year"></select>
                                                                  <input id="form-widgets-datetime_added-calendar" class="form.widgets.datetime_added-calendar date" type="hidden" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-calendar" originalvalue="" value="05/18/2015"/>
                                                                  <span id="form-widgets-datetime_added-timecomponents" class="datetimewidget-time">
                                                                        <select id="form-widgets-datetime_added-hour" class="hour datetime-widget required datetime-field" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-hour"></select>
                                                                        <span class="separator">:</span>
                                                                        <select id="form-widgets-datetime_added-minute" class="minute datetime-widget required datetime-field" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-minute"></select>
                                                                        <input type="hidden" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-timezone" originalvalue=""/>
                                                                        </span>
                                                                  <input type="hidden" value="1" name="form.widgets.datetime_added-empty-marker" originalvalue="1"/>
                                                            </div>
                                                      </li>
                                                      <li>
                                                            <div id="formfield-form-widgets-image" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.image empty" data-fieldname="form.widgets.image">
                                                                  <label class="horizontal" for="form-widgets-image">Image</label>
                                                                  <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                                                  <span id="form-widgets-image" class="named-image-widget namedblobimage-field">
                                                                        <input id="form-widgets-image-input" type="file" name="form.widgets.image"/>
                                                                  </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                      </li>
                                                </ul>
                                                
                                                
                                                
                                                
                                                <div id="formfield-form-widgets-message" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.message empty" data-fieldname="form.widgets.message">
                                                      <label class="horizontal" for="form-widgets-message">Message</label>
                                                      <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                                      <textarea id="form-widgets-message" class="textarea-widget text-field" name="form.widgets.message"></textarea>
                                                </div>
                                          </fieldset>
                                          <!--
                                      
                                           Secondary fieldsets 
                                      
                                          -->
                                          <fieldset id="fieldset-settings" class="kssattr-fieldset-settings formPanel" data-fieldset="settings" style="display: none;">
                                              <legend id="fieldsetlegend-settings" style="visibility: hidden; font-size: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 0px; width: 0px; line-height: 0;">
                                      
                                                  Settings
                                      
                                              </legend>
                                              <div id="formfield-form-widgets-IExcludeFromNavigation-exclude_from_nav" class="field z3cformInlineValidation kssattr-fieldname-form.widgets.IExcludeFromNavigation.exclude_from_nav" data-fieldname="form.widgets.IExcludeFromNavigation.exclude_from_nav">
                                                  <span id="form-widgets-IExcludeFromNavigation-exclude_from_nav" class="option">
                                                      <input id="form-widgets-IExcludeFromNavigation-exclude_from_nav-0" class="single-checkbox-widget required bool-field" type="checkbox" value="selected" name="form.widgets.IExcludeFromNavigation.exclude_from_nav:list" originalvalue="selected"/>
                                                      <label for="form-widgets-IExcludeFromNavigation-exclude_from_nav-0">
                                                          <span class="label">
                                      
                                                              Exclude from navigation
                                      
                                                          </span>
                                                      </label>
                                                  </span>
                                                  <input type="hidden" value="1" name="form.widgets.IExcludeFromNavigation.exclude_from_nav-empty-marker" originalvalue="1"/>
                                                  <div class="formHelp">
                                      
                                                      If selected, this item will not appear in the navi…
                                      
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div class="fieldErrorBox"></div>
                                              </div>
                                          </fieldset>
                                          <div class="formControls">
                                              <input id="form-buttons-save" class="submit-widget button-field context button tiny" type="submit" value="Save" name="form.buttons.save"/>
                                              <input id="form-buttons-cancel" class="submit-widget button-field standalone button tiny" type="submit" value="Cancel" name="form.buttons.cancel"/>
                                          </div>

                                    </form>
                              </div><!--end comment form-->
                              
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </section>
            
      </div><!--end color page container-->




    <!--  <img tal:attributes="src string:${context/absolute_url}/@@download/picture/${picture/filename};
                         height picture/_height | nothing;
                         width picture/_width | nothing;"
        /> -->

